      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 127,
      "message": "k8s makes similar variables available for Cloudify Manager port and address.  (In ONAP, CM runs in k8s.) There really isn't a difference.\n\nThe CLOUDIFY variable that you're proposing overlaps with existing variables that convey the same information.  \n\nSince there is already a solution for providing DH configuration in Consul for the Dublin release, maybe the best way forward is to drop the \"useConsul\" changes for now and revisit it later.",
